      "text": "Preeks un Lihgminba irr\nno ta augliga Tthruma/ no tahs\nMoaba Semines atremte/ es\natrauschu to Wihnu no teem\nWihna-Spatdeem/ tur ne taps\nWihna-Ohgas mihtas ar Pree-\nku-Dseefmahm/ sta Gawilescha-\nna ta Breeziga ne buhs wairs\npreeziga/"
    },
    {
      "n": 34,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tahs Brehfschanas deht\nno Esbona lihds Eelealei/\nlihds\nJakzai irr tee fawu Balsfi pa-\nzehluscht/ no Zoaras lihds Oro-\nnaimam to trejn Gaddu Gohwi/\njo ir tee Uhdeni no Nimrima\ntaps pohsta."
    },
    {
      "n": 35,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un es isnihzinaschu\neekth Moaba/ fakka tas KUNGS/\ntohs/ kas us Augstumeem up-\npure/ un tohs/ kas fatweem Dee-\nweem kwehpina."
    },
    {
      "n": 36,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tadeht ruhz manna\nSirds pahr Moabu ka Stabu-\nles/ ir manna Sirds duhz ka\nStabules pahr teem Laudim no\nKiteres/ jo tee irr pahr leeku tur-\nrejschees/ tapehz irr teem bohja\nja-eet."
    },
    {
      "n": 37,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Jo wiꞥſch Galivas buhs\nplikas/ un wiꞥſch Bahrdas no-\ndsihtas/ us wiꞥſchm Rohkahin\nbuhs eegraisitas Sihtes/ un us\nteam Gurneem buhs Matfs."
    },
    {
      "n": 38,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Us wiꞥſchm Moaba Jum-\nteem/ un us wiꞥſchm winnu\nGelahm waidehs/ jo es esmu\nMoabu tadaufijs/ itt ka weenu"
    },
    {
      "n": 39,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Ka irr wiꞥſch istrubj\nnahts/ ka tee kanz/ ka atgreeſ\nMoabs to Pakansu Kannā ta-\npis? ta buhs Moabs witfeen\nkas apkahrt winnu irr/ par A-\nstmeekli un par Istruhzinasch-\nnu."
    },
    {
      "n": 40,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Jo ta fakka tas KUNGS\nRedsi/ wiꞥſch ahtri skaida\nEhrglis/ un wiꞥſch isplehti-\nfawus Spahrnus pahr Moab"
    },
    {
      "n": 41,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tee Pilstahti irr ugiwa-\nreti/ un tee Stiprumi irr u-\nxeunti/ un ta Sirds to Wa-\nrenu no Moaba buhs tai De-\nnā/ ka ta Sirds weenas Se-\nwas/ kas Behrnu Sahp-\nzeetsch."
    },
    {
      "n": 42,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Jo Moabs taps tsd-\ndehts/ ka tas Tanta wairs\npaleek/ jo wiꞥſch irr prett\nKUNGS pa angstinajees."
    },
    {
      "n": 43,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Bihjaschana/ un Bedr-\nun Walgs pahr tewi/ ak tu E-\ndshwotajs no Moaba! takka ta-\nKUNGS."
    },
    {
      "n": 44,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Kas no Bihjaschanas\nbehg/ tas krittibs Bedrē/un\nno Bedres istkahpj/ tas ta-\nWalga guhstihts/ jo es wed-\nschu pahr Moabu to Gad-\nwinnu Peemekleſchanas/ fat-\ntas KUNGS."
    },
    {
      "n": 45,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Kas no Pahrwarresch-\nnas behg/ tee stahivehs appak-\ntahs Ehnas no Esbona/ bet\nEsbona iseeg ugauns/ un w-\nua Leesma no Siena/un opr-\nMi"
